# 止蝕
(pos:動詞)
<explanation>
yue:喺投資、賭博等活動入面，當輸到一定程度，為咗唔使再輸更多，而決定停止繼續投入，或者賣出手上嘅投資品。通常指喺蝕錢嘅情況下，盡快結束，減少損失。
eng:to cut one's losses; to stop further losses
<eg>
yue:見股市跌到咁犀利，我決定止蝕，賣晒啲股票。 (gin3 gu2 si5 dit3 dou3 gam3 sai1 lei6, ngo5 git3 ding6 ji2 sik1, maai6 saai3 di1 gu2 piu3.)
eng:Seeing the stock market falling so sharply, I decided to cut my losses and sold all my stocks.

yue:輸咗咁多錢，不如依家止蝕算數，唔好再玩落去。 (syu1 zo2 gam3 do1 cin2, bat1 jyu4 ga1 ji2 sik1 syun3 syu6, m4 hou2 zai3 waan2 lok6 heoi3.)
eng:Having lost so much money, it's better to cut your losses now and stop playing.
